o-abuse-victims-so-far-inquiry-shows|title=Australian Catholic church has paid $276m to abuse victims so far, inquiry shows|first=Australian Associated|last=Press|date=2017-02-16|accessdate=2017-10-29|website=Theguardian.com|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206015505/https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2017/feb/16/australian-catholic-church-has-paid-276m-to-abuse-victims-so-far-inquiry-shows|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="abc.net.au">{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-02-06/child-sex-abuse-royal-commission:-data-reveals-catholic-abuse/8243890|title=Worst Catholic groups for child sex abuse claims in Australia revealed|date=2017-02-06|website=Abc.net.au|accessdate=2017-10-29|archive-date=2017-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214091022/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-02-06/child-sex-abuse-royal-commission:-data-reveals-catholic-abuse/8243890|dead-url=no}}</ref>1980年至2015年間，經營多個住宅設施的基督教兄弟公司向受害者支付的賠款金額最高，為763人總計賠償4850萬美元。<ref name=settlementoz />

